headlines.description: Arsenal missed out on their chance to get back into the Premier League's top four after a 3-1 loss to Wolves at Molineux on Wednesday night.

video.headline: Wolves wound woeful Arsenal's top 4 hunt

headlines.shortLinkText: Arsenal's top-four hopes take hit with Wolves loss

headlines.description: Manchester City went back to the top of the Premier League and inflicted yet another defeat on Manchester United with a 2-0 win at Old Trafford.

video.headline: Man City 3 wins from title after derby victory
